{"id":231123523,"title":"#問 我的玻璃吸管怎麼了？","content":"之前因為看了海龜的影片覺得太殘忍了\n於是去年就和朋友一起用蝦皮團購玻璃吸管\n\n某天在學校清洗的時候發現彎曲的地方\n居然出現一條黑黑的污漬???\n用刷子來回刷了好多次還是刷不掉\n試著用一咪咪ㄉ洗碗精刷也才淡掉一點點而已\n\n但想請問版上大大的彎吸管\n有沒有跟我一樣有這個狀況??\n上網爬文都沒有看到類似的文章(;´༎ຶД༎ຶ`)\n\n通常我喝完飲料就會去做清洗\n難道是黴菌嗎⋯ಠ_ಠ？\n\n以下附圖\nhttps://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg\n\n再來是我用微距鏡頭拍的\n上面那張是剛用刷子來回刷完 \n下面那張是大概過了一下下\n（感覺又變黑的趨勢⋯）\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Aq7WbTO.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/LHp1pRr.jpg","excerpt":"之前因為看了海龜的影片覺得太殘忍了，於是去年就和朋友一起用蝦皮團購玻璃吸管，某天在學校清洗的時候發現彎曲的地方，居然出現一條黑黑的污漬？？？用刷子來回刷了好多次還是刷不掉，試著用一咪咪ㄉ洗碗精刷也才淡掉一點點而已","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-04-19T12:52:52.670Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-19T12:52:52.670Z","commentCount":10,"likeCount":45,"tags":[],"topics":["環保","玻璃吸管"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立臺北護理健康大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":45}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Aq7WbTO.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/LHp1pRr.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9cff7497-2cbb-476c-ac3b-562cbc11b962","url":"https://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-19T12:52:52.670Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-19T12:52:52.670Z"},{"id":"9cff7497-2cbb-476c-ac3b-562cbc11b962","url":"https://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/QIVyt4t.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-19T12:52:52.670Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-19T12:52:52.670Z"